result.purpose: This folder contains mock implementations of various interfaces for testing purposes.
result.architecture: The folder follows a modular architecture pattern, where each file provides a mock implementation of a specific interface, facilitating unit testing.

mocks/handlers/quest.go.purpose: This file defines a mock implementation of the Quest interface for testing purposes.

mocks/handlers/quest_action.go.purpose: This file defines a mock implementation of the QuestAction interface for testing purposes.

mocks/handlers/quest_reward.go.purpose: This file defines a mock implementation for the QuestReward interface used in testing.

mocks/handlers/reward.go.purpose: This file provides a mock implementation of the Reward type for testing purposes.

mocks/handlers/sponsor.go.purpose: This file defines a mock implementation of the Sponsor interface for testing purposes.

mocks/handlers/user.go.purpose: This file defines a mock implementation of the User interface for testing purposes.

mocks/handlers/user_quest.go.purpose: This file provides a mock implementation for the UserQuest interface, enabling testing of its methods.

mocks/handlers/user_reward.go.purpose: This file defines a mock implementation of the UserReward interface for testing purposes.
